=94 so there can be an informed vote. Also there are ways to have some sort=
 of adjustment mechanism =E2=80=94 mainly =E2=80=9Ccontingent value rights,=
=E2=80=9D where the target shareholders get their regular payment plus some=
 extra thing that is worth more or less depending on the target=E2=80=99s b=
usiness results, etc. =E2=80=94 but they are not that common and don=E2=80=
=99t tend to focus on things like cash at closing.


