. There may be some more specific disclosure of the target=E2=80=99s fee ar=
rangements =E2=80=94=C2=A0there normally=C2=A0<em>is </em>specific disclosu=
re of its=C2=A0<em>bankers=E2=80=99=C2=A0</em>fee arrangements =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0at signing, so if the target tells the buyer at signing =E2=80=9Cwe have=
 agreed to pay our lawyers $10 million=E2=80=9D and then pays them $90 mill=
ion there might be a breach of the covenant. (Though, again, the remedy for=
